Content: Medical Medium Info Shall Not Lie! Is This WikiPedia Info about Raspberries & Blackberries true? MEs been Robbied of AWholistic Blackberry Pie as her & her children's Life! "A raspberry is an aggregate fruit, developing from the numerous distinct carpels of a single flower.[4] What distinguishes the raspberry from its blackberry relatives is whether or not the torus (receptacle or stem) "picks with" (i.e., stays with) the fruit. When picking a blackberry fruit, the torus stays with the fruit. With a raspberry, the torus remains on the plant, leaving a hollow core in the raspberry fruit.[5]"Medical Medium Info? 🍇💭🫡〰️🙏🛐🛡️😈⛓️‍
